@startuml
hide footbox
actor 仓管员
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "StockAllotOrderController" as Controller
participant "StockAllotOrderServiceImpl" as Service
database "MySQL数据库" as DB

仓管员 -> Frontend: 点击新增，填写调拨信息
Frontend -> Frontend: 表单验证

Frontend -> Controller: POST /stock/allotOrder
Controller -> Controller: 权限校验，校验仓库不同

Controller -> Service: insertStockAllotOrder(username, allotOrder)
Service -> Service: 生成调拨单号，设置状态

group 处理调拨明细
  Service -> Service: 设置每条明细的单号、仓库编码、行号
end

Service -> DB: 批量插入调拨明细
DB --> Service: 返回插入结果

Service -> DB: 插入调拨单主表
DB --> Service: 返回影响行数

Service --> Controller: 返回结果
Controller --> Frontend: 返回AjaxResult响应
Frontend --> 仓管员: 显示创建成功

@enduml